Interface Member

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Comparable, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    BaseMember, EntityMember, Member

    public interface Member
extends Comparable, Serializable

    Member records membership in an AuthzGroup; user, role, and flags.
